{"tid":1944376,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"生化危機 3 重製版保險箱密碼為「918」　中國玩家感覺冒犯揚言抵制","createTime":"2020-03-26T10:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T05:39:43.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a2f5944703a9f12285156a668d6a0af79d0f2c14","tid":1944376,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ae5924c0-6db4-11ea-a6fd-84401f5f4161-scaled.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2Fae5924c0-6db4-11ea-a6fd-84401f5f4161-scaled.jpeg&h=657a4da9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日 Capcom 推出了《生化危機 3 重製版》的試玩版，以讓大家體驗重製版與舊作的分別。不過，有中國玩家遊玩過後指，遊戲內的密碼數字有冒犯中國之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n《生化危機 3 重製版》試玩版的遊玩時間只有 5 分鐘左右，當中有個關卡需要在保險箱上輸入密碼，而密碼提示印在一張海報上，玩家推測後可得出三位密碼「918」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-03-26-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.10.50-1280x576.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-03-26-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884.10.50-1280x576.png&h=b91930d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-03-26-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.08.42-1280x458.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-03-26-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884.08.42-1280x458.png&h=54c81251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-03-26-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.09.18-1280x720.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-03-26-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884.09.18-1280x720.png&h=bbca5ad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，不少中國玩家與台灣玩家都認為這件事情過於牽強，並質疑是否與中國歷史有關的數字，如「64」、「128」等都通通不能使用，指某部份中國玩家過於「玻璃心」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-03-26-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%884.15.42-869x900.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-03-26-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25884.15.42-869x900.png&h=1512d1a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/03/26/biohazard-re3-918/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F03%2F26%2Fbiohazard-re3-918%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR7ScfX6drAaaDYLMstvIIS4%3D&h=e4f187ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/03/26/biohazard-re3-918/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"f0d57e6940608d0894e2b56d23ac30ae0d138c4f","tid":1944376,"uid":51977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:59:17.000Z","msg":"狗改不了吃屎，最後又咪係真香定律"},{"pid":"ca14c5f8bead2a4313b8d31a019ccb3ea3c46fea","tid":1944376,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:10:53.000Z","msg":"咪撚玩攞傻閪"},{"pid":"6c4e212808fd8dd6b85c037169bfc25efa5ff4f5","tid":1944376,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:17:54.000Z","msg":"4條1 314 214又話冒犯單身狗<br />\n911冒犯美帝<br />\n311冒犯日本<br />\n不能盡錄結論唔好玩密碼鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a424c83ed8e9e8f3cca0ed68a4cee25181aa527","tid":1944376,"uid":155784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:39:43.000Z","msg":"咁721啦"}]}